### Test all API routes
### This file contains requests to test all routes in the VoiceScribe API
### Make sure to set SKIP_AUTH=true environment variable before testing

### Authentication routes (no auth required even with SKIP_AUTH=false)
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/auth/validate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "token": "test_token"
}

